{"word":"H4339 - מֵישָׁר - mêyshâr - may-shawr' - Agreement","slug":"H4339","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מֵישָׁר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mêyshâr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>may-shawr'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Agreement"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D9;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E8; - me&#x0302;ysha&#x0302;r</b> - <i>may-shawr'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H3474\">H3474</a>; <i>evenness</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>prosperity</i> or <i>concord</i>; also <i>straightness</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>rectitude</i> (only in plural with singular sense; often adverbially): - agreement, aright, that are equal, equity, (things that are) right (-eously, things), sweetly, upright (-ly, -ness)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3474\">H3474</a>, <a href=\"#/H3475\">H3475</a>, <a href=\"#/H3476\">H3476</a>, <a href=\"#/H3477\">H3477</a>, <a href=\"#/H3483\">H3483</a>, <a href=\"#/H3484\">H3484</a>, <a href=\"#/H4334\">H4334</a>, <a href=\"#/H8289\">H8289</a>, <a href=\"#/H8290\">H8290</a>"}]}